{"tid":1958034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国扯半旗悼亡者 外交部堅發言人：來世還做中国人","createTime":"2020-04-04T10:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T16:33:00.000Z","uid":184679,"like":53,"dislike":213,"uniUserReply":147,"replies":[{"pid":"ac7a8a2ebf40d0a42c916f4a3f1a73a6f9184024","tid":1958034,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T10:39:50.000Z","msg":"中國爆發武漢肺炎疫情，死亡人數眾多，中國今天舉行全國悼念活動，各場所紛紛下半旗，全國停止所有公共娛樂活動。對此，中國外交部發言人趙立堅也在推特向逝者致哀，還說，「此生無悔入華夏，來世還做中國人！」<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，中國今天舉行全國性哀悼活動，全國各地和駐外使館下半旗致哀，同時全面停止公共娛樂行為。此外，今天上午10點，中國全體人民共同默哀3分鐘，汽車、火車、郵輪同時鳴笛，並鳴響防空警報。<br />\n<br />\n這是2010年8月15日哀悼甘肅省舟曲土石流事件後，中國再次舉辦全國性哀悼活動。當土石流事件中有1557人罹難、284人失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n對此，中國外交部發言人趙立堅在推特PO文說，在4月4日哀悼日之際，謹向英雄致敬，向逝者致哀，沉痛哀悼新冠肺炎疫情期間犧牲烈士、逝世同胞。「此生無悔入華夏，來世還做中國人！銘記歷史，不忘英雄！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3123007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3123007&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD25ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=cc13e6cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3123007&h=103e6fa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3123007</a>"},{"pid":"94c75be6f0f217830253a3280af7f4a8d74510b3","tid":1958034,"uid":111811,"like":436,"dislike":4,"score":432,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T10:40:29.000Z","msg":"最毒咀咒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1380294830faf6a694aa4e5e3179e6f31c7cc1b9","tid":1958034,"uid":68463,"like":216,"dislike":3,"score":213,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T10:41:17.000Z","msg":"好撚毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1211717eb3c92dce76b2189db7c1138a4c246cd7","tid":1958034,"uid":72185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"94c75be6f0f217830253a3280af7f4a8d74510b3","tid":1958034,"uid":111811,"like":436,"dislike":4,"score":432,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T10:40:29.0