<br />\n綜合中媒報導，中國今天舉行全國性哀悼活動，全國各地和駐外使館下半旗致哀，同時全面停止公共娛樂行為。此外，今天上午10點，中國全體人民共同默哀3分鐘，汽車、火車、郵輪同時鳴笛，並鳴響防空警報。<br />\n<br />\n這是2010年8月15日哀悼甘肅省舟曲土石流事件後，中國再次舉辦全國性哀悼活動。當土石流事件中有1557人罹難、284人失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n對此，中國外交部發言人趙立堅在推特PO文說，在4月4日哀悼日之際，謹向英雄致敬，向逝者致哀，沉痛哀悼新冠肺炎疫情期間犧牲烈士、逝世同胞。「此生無悔入華夏，來世還做中國人！銘記歷史，不忘英雄！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3123007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3123007&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD25ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=cc13e6cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3123007&h=103e6fa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3123007</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T10:43:32.000Z","msg":"來世還做中國人!<br />\n呢個感嘆號成個意思唔同哂啵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T11:15:19.000Z","msg":"來世還做中國人?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21539a3fd622209bd5307e342b87cf4d69ee26d","tid":1958034,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T11:15:54.000Z","msg":"華你老母夏咩"},{"pid":"e21919564e185eff4b20f6d80c46c88d3a2b9185","tid":1958034,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T11:16:02.000Z","msg":"毒過咀咒人地全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97db05c19114007a34df6202fafe5b157a55331f","tid":1958034,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T11:16:07.000Z","msg":"把口毒撚到咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d006df7965b6cf700a63e4fee04474ad07887a","tid":1958034,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T11:16:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf0f92b996de00a27a7b390255f5bbb182e86b29","tid":1958034,